library(tidyverse)
library(p8105.datasets)
library(plotly)
rest_inspec = 
  p8105.datasets::rest_inspec |> 
  drop_na(grade, score) |> 
  filter(grade %in% c('A', 'B', 'C')) |> 
  mutate(
    year_month = str_sub(inspection_date, 0, 7),
    year = year(inspection_date),
    month = year(inspection_date))
rest_inspec$grade |> unique()
## [1] "A" "B" "C"
rest_inspec$action |> unique()
## [1] "Violations were cited in the following area(s)."            
## [2] "No violations were recorded at the time of this inspection."
## [3] "Establishment re-opened by DOHMH"
rest_inspec |> 
  filter(boro != 'Missing') |> 
  plot_ly(y =  ~score, type = 'box', x = ~boro, color = ~boro)
head(rest_inspec)

rest_inspec |> 
  count(grade) |> 
  plot_ly(x = ~grade, y = ~n, color = ~grade, type = "bar")
rest_inspec |>
  group_by(year_month) |> 
  count(grade) |> 
  plot_ly(x = ~year_month, y = ~n, color = ~grade, type = 'scatter', mode = 'markers')
